---
const pillars = [
  {
    icon: "vote",
    title: "Democratic Control",
    description: "One member, one vote. You help decide which features we build and how the platform is run."
  },
  {
    icon: "transparency",
    title: "Radical Transparency",
    description: "Every dollar of membership dues is visible on our open ledger. You know exactly where your money goes."
  },
  {
    icon: "data",
    title: "Data Sovereignty",
    description: "You own your data. We don't sell it, and you can take your entire social graph with you if you ever choose to leave."
  }
];
---

<section class="coop">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="reveal">The Kith & Kin Cooperative</h2>
    <p class="coop-intro reveal reveal-delay-1">
      Most social platforms are built to serve shareholders. Kith & Kin is built to serve its members.
      By choosing a platform cooperative model, we've legally and technically locked our values into the foundation of the app.
    </p>

    <div class="pillars">
      {pillars.map((pillar, index) => (
        <div class={`pillar reveal reveal-delay-${index + 1}`}>
          <div class="pillar-icon" data-icon={pillar.icon}>
            {pillar.icon === "vote" && (
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"></path>
                <polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"></polyline>
              </svg>
            )}
            {pillar.icon === "transparency" && (
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
                <line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12" y2="12"></line>
                <line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12.01" y2="8"></line>
              </svg>
            )}
            {pillar.icon === "data" && (
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
                <path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"></path>
              </svg>
            )}
          </div>
          <h3>{pillar.title}</h3>
          <p>{pillar.description}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <div class="coop-box reveal">
      <div class="coop-box-header">
        <span class="coop-box-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
            <path d="M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3"></path>
            <line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"></line>
          </svg>
        </span>
        <h3>Why a Cooperative?</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="coop-box-content">
        <p>
          We believe that social technology shaped by venture capital will always prioritize engagement over well-being,
          growth over community, and shareholders over users.
        </p>
        <p>
          A platform cooperative is a different kind of company—one where the people who use the platform also own it.
          There are no outside investors pushing for infinite growth. No board meetings about how to extract more attention.
          No pivot to ads when the money runs low.
        </p>
        <p>
          Instead, we answer to our members. When you join as a member-owner, you're not just a user—you're a stakeholder
          with a real vote in how this platform evolves. That's the foundation we think social technology needs.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .coop {
    background-color: var(--white);
    padding: var(--space-3xl) 0;
  }

  .coop h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .coop-intro {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-2xl);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .pillars {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .pillar {
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .pillar-icon {
    width: 72px;
    height: 72px;
    background: var(--sage-light);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-md);
    color: var(--sage);
  }

  .pillar h3 {
    color: var(--text-dark);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .pillar p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .coop-box {
    background: var(--cream-light);
    border: 2px solid var(--sage-light);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    margin-top: var(--space-2xl);
    max-width: 720px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(31, 41, 33, 0.05);
  }

  .coop-box-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-md);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .coop-box-icon {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    background: var(--sage-light);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--sage);
  }

  .coop-box-header h3 {
    color: var(--text-dark);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .coop-box-content p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .coop-box-content p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .pillars {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-lg);
    }

    .pillar {
      padding: var(--space-md);
    }

    .coop-box {
      padding: var(--space-lg);
    }
  }
</style>
